public interface Descriptor
extends Externalizable

ChemicalStructureAnnotation – 2011.09.05
Defines an annotated property of short/long description and an index. Note the index is not unique to Descriptors but should be to it's sub-class (e.g. Annotation, Observation, Identifier)
